  <name>SpeedyNote</name>
  <summary>Fast note-taking application with PDF annotation support</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>
      SpeedyNote is a powerful and intuitive note-taking application designed for speed and efficiency. 
      It features pressure-sensitive inking, PDF background integration, and controller support for 
      natural handwriting experiences.
    </p>
    <p>Key features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pressure-sensitive handwriting with stylus support</li>
      <li>PDF background integration for annotation</li>
      <li>Controller input support for enhanced interaction</li>
      <li>Multiple drawing tools (pen, marker, eraser)</li>
      <li>Markdown editing capabilities</li>
      <li>Export to various formats</li>
      <li>Multi-language support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
